==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bromeliaceous
<hw>Bro*me`li*a"ceous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Named
after Olaf <ets>Bromel</ets>, a Swedish botanist.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or resembling, a family of
endogenous and mostly epiphytic or saxicolous plants of which the genera
<gen>Tillandsia</gen> and <gen>Billbergia</gen> are examples. The
pineapple, though terrestrial, is also of this family.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bromic</ent>⟦br⟧
